            <title>[CASSANDRA-20420] InterceptingExecutor.schedule returns a simulator-unsafe Future</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-20420</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The FutureTask we return must be a type sourced from the InstanceClassLoader, rather than the system class loader - which does not apply byte weaving, and so does not intercept e.g. Object.wait.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
